6 May 2016The Minister of Communications Ms Faith Muthambi will table the Budget Vote of the Department of Communications in the National Assembly, Cape Town on Friday, 6th May 2016. Minister Muthambi will in her speech outline some of the successes of the past year; how entities in her portfolio delivered on key strategic objectives and outline their plans for the 2016/17 financial year.The Departmental Budget Vote will take place as follows: Date: Friday, 06 May 2016 Time: 10h00 Venue: National Assembly, Parliament, Cape Town Enquiries: Mish Molakeng Cell: 082 469 3997 Issued by Government Communication and Information System on behalf of The Department of Communications